				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Should victims be able to attack their bounty hunter or should they only be able to attack in self-defense (Bounty Hunter must make first attack as per rules of a challenger of a duel)? i BELIEVE sINCE THE IDEA IS BEING HUNTER AND NOT BEING CHALLENEGED. THE BOUNTY HUNTER SHOULD a) HAVE FIRST STIKE. b) HAVE SOME SORT OF BONUS.  aFTER ALL WOULD BE SAD IF YOU ARE A BOUNTY HUNTER AND GET YOUR TARGET, BUT FING YOUR TARGET CAN WASTE YOU EVERYTIME YOU TRY TO COLLECT. sO IF THE HUNTER GETS SOME SORT OF BONUS WHEN IN COMBAT WITH THE TARGET HE WILL HAVE A BETTER CHANCE TO COLECT, ALSO THIS WOULD ENTICE THE TARGET TO RUN, WHICH WOULD ADD TO CONTINUITY.
<br />
Should victims know who their bounty hunter is? NO, DID HAN SOLO KNOW EXACTLY WHO WAS HUNTING THE MELINIUM FALCON? NOPE. BOUNTY HUNTERS NEED A SENCE OF SUPRISE. A TARGET SHOULD KNOW HE HAS A BOUNTY ON HIS HEAD, BUT SHOULD NOT KNOW ANYTHING ELSE. THIS WAY IT WILL ADD TO THE ROLEPLAY OF THE SYSTEM AND ADD CONTENT.
<br />
What would you like to see in the Bounty Hunter system? I WOULD LIKE TO SEE SOME SORT OF TRACKING SYSTEM FOR THE BOUNTY HUNTER THAT MAKES IT POSSIBLE TO FIND TARGETS FROM SHORT AND LONG DISTANCES, BUT DOES NOT MAKE IT "EASY". ALSO TO ADD CONTINUITY, THE TARGET SHOULD BE MORE INCLINED TO RUN THEN TO STAY AND FIGHT, SO FOR EXAMPLE, WHEN BOUNTY HUNTER LOCATES HIS TARGET THE TARGET DOES NOT KNOW WHO IS AFTER HIM. SO THE BOUNTY HUNTER HAS AN ELEMENT OF SUPRISE, OR A CHANCE FOR SNIPEING THE TARGET. WHEN HUNTER FINDS TARGET, HE SHOULD BE THE ONLY ONE ALLOUD TO INITIATE COMBAT AND NOONE SHOULD BE ALLOUD TO INTERFERE, KINDA LIKE THE TWO PLAYERS ARE DUELING AND ARE IMMUNE TO OUTSIDE INTERACTION VIA PLAYERS AND NPCS. THE BOUNTY HUNTER SHOULD HAVE SOME TYPE OF BONUS WHEN IN COMBAT WITH HIS TARGET. THUS AGAIN MAKEING THE TARGET PREFUR RUNNING TO STANDING AND FIGHTING. ONCE BOUNTY HUNTER KILLS HIS TARGET AND GETS CREDITED THE MONEY TO HIS ACCOUNT. IF THE TARGET MANAGES TO KILL THE HUNTER EVEN WHEN THE ODDS ARE STACKED VERY MUCH SO AGAINST HIM, THE HUNTER SHOULD AUTOMATICALLY LOOSE HIS MISSION AND THE CONTRACT IS UP FOR GRABS AGAIN. 
<br />
What do you think would cause problems in the Bounty Hunter system? BIGGEST PROBLEM i SEE IS THE TARGET GETTING FRIENDS TO PROTECT HIM SO WHENEVER A HUNTER GETS CLOSE THE FRIENDS AND THE TARGET WASTE THE HUNTER THEIRFOR MAKEING IT IMPOSSIBLE TO COLLECT. AND THEREFOR MAKEING THE ENTIRE CAT AND MOUSE GAME OF THE BOUNTYHUNTER PROFESSION NO FUN. AND NOT HAVEING BOUNTY HUNTERS IN STAR WARS WOULD REMOVE A CERTAIN TYPE OF AUTHORITY AND LEAVE THE CONTINUITY KIND OF EMPTY. SO THERE SHOULD BE STRICK CODED GUILDLINES FOR THE BOUNTYHUNTER LIKE HOW I MENTIONED THE HUNTER AND TARGET SHOULD BE IMMUNE TO OUTSIDE INFLUENCE WHEN IN COMBAT.
<br />
AND THE BONUS TO THE HUNTER DURIN COMBAT SHOULD NOT THROW OFF BALANCE BUT SHOULD GIVE ENOUGH TO MAKE IT DIFFICULT FOR THE HUNTER TO BE KILLED BY THE PLAYER. THIS SHOULD ONLY BE A BONUS WHEN THE HUNTER ENGAGES THE TARGET FOR WHICH HE HAS A OPEN CONTRACT FOR. ALSO THOUGH i AM UNSURE HOW THE LVLING SUSTEM WORKS AND HOW ONE PLAYER MMORE POWERFUL WOULD STACK UP TO A NEW PLAYER UNTRAINED AND LESS POWERFUL. THE HUNTER SHOULD BE MATCHED UP WITH AVAILABLE TARGETS BASED HOW DIFFICULT THE TARGET WOULD BE KILL FOR THE HUNTER. THEY SHOULD NEITHER BE TOO HARD NOR TOO EASY. 
<br />

<br />
just my ideas on this. I hope they help  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" border="0" />
<br />
ans at least feed others for better ideas and thoughts.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
